  "name": "RPlog_The_Republic_Retreats",
  "title": "The Trap Springs at Cochran",
  "summary": "Over the planet Cochran, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin's Imperial fleet, having already shattered the trapped Griffon Fleet and its sacrificed flagship Gabriel, turns to grind down a newly arrived Republic fleet led by the captured Victory-class destroyer Reprisal. From his medical bed, Kreldin merges his first and second battlegroups into a brawling melee and springs his trump card, summoning Admiral Talkor's second Imperial armada and the dreadnought Predator out of hyperspace to encircle the rebels. Imperial bomber pilots Krieg and Tellain pound the Reprisal's bridge with missile salvos, while the TIE ace Jal'Dana Rall refuels and rejoins the fighter screen, dueling Republic pilots like Gene, Hase, and Crystal in Ghost 2. As the Reprisal's shields collapse and the captains Richardson and Caiton press the attack, the Republic captain finally orders a full retreat, and the rebel fighters break off and flee the doomed system.",
